data.description: PAID SOLAR!! Beautiful Custom Home with 2.39 Acres. Bring your RV, Horses & Toys. Featuring an 1800 sq.ft Workshop with 14ft & 12ft Doors. Spacious 4100 sq.ft Home with 7 Bedrooms, 4 Bathrooms, Large Bonus Room, Media Room or Office. Downstairs Features a Large Master Bedroom with Fireplace, Large Walk-In Closet, Bath with Jacuzzi Tub & an Oversized Shower. Two Additional Bedrooms & Guest Bathroom. Upstairs Features a Large Master Bedroom Upstairs with a Large Walk-In Closet, a Large Loft, & # Additional Oversized Bedrooms. Kitchen with Custom Babinetry, Breakfast Bar, Built-In Microwave & Walk-In Pantry. Some Addition Features Include, Pergo Wood Flooring, Neutral Carpeting, Central Vacuum System , Ceiling Fans Throughout, Duel Heating & Air & so Much More.
